:30.58,"time_end":36.73},{"position":14,"content":"Great. Thanks.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-18-test-1-part-1-2023-06-16-20-37-03/15.mp3","time_start":36.82,"time_end":38.35},{"position":15,"content":"Is that in Wells?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-18-test-1-part-1-2023-06-16-20-37-03/16.mp3","time_start":38.65,"time_end":40.29},{"position":16,"content":"No it's actually in Harborne.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-18-test-1-part-1-2023-06-16-20-37-03/17.mp3","time_start":40.29,"time_end":43.21},{"position":17,"content":"Wells isn't far from there, though.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-18-test-1-part-1-2023-06-16-20-37-03/18.mp3","time_start":43.21,"time_end":45.58},{"position":18,"content":"I really like that area.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-18-test-1-part-1-2023-06-16-20-37-03/19.mp3","time_start":45.58,"time_end":47.63},{"position":19,"content":"My grandmother lived there when I was a kid.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-18-test-1-part-1-2023-06-16-20-37-03/20.mp3","time_start":47.63,"time_end":50.32},{"position":20,"content":"Yes, it is nice.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-18-test-1-part-1-2023-06-16-20-37-03/21.mp3","time_start":50.5,"time_end":52.69},{"position":21,"content":"Right, so now I want to ask you some questions about how you travelled here today.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-18-test-1-part-1-2023-06-16-20-37-03/22.mp3","time_start":52.89,"time_end":58.94},{"position":22,"content":"Did you use public transport?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-18-test-1-part-1-2023-06-16-20-37-03/23.mp3","time_start":59.27,"ti